Select    S.ScreenID, OVI.VeriIslemAdi, OM.ITObjectName,LIO.ITObjectID, LIO.Tarih,  LIO.InfoParams, LIO.InfoKayit, *
From        RN100_LogsITObjects LIO
            Left Outer Join RN100_ObjectsVeriIslemleri OVI On OVI.ITVeriIslemID = LIO.ITVeriIslemID
            Left Outer Join RN100_ObjectsM OM On OM.ITObjectID = LIO.ITObjectID
            Left Outer Join RN100_ObjectsM OMSP On OMSP.ITObjectID = OVI.SPITObjectID
			Left Outer Join dbo.RN100_Screens S On S.ITObjectID = OM.ITObjectID
Where       LIO.InfoKayit Like '%ZCFC872FX0D746764%'
Order By    LIO.ITObjectsLogID Desc
